review_blob: What can be said about this beer that hasnt already been stated. Its dark, smooth, and tastes damn good. Not overwhelming, but not weak, its just right, feels great and fishes even better.
One of my favs to fall back on when there is nothing better around. Its atleast a decent beer. Not bad at all for a mainstream beer. Staple in my book.
First time in years, I couldnt even get myself to finish the bottle. Lime made it a little better, but still not what I like.
